cff-version: 1.2.0
message: If you use this work, please cite it using the metadata below.
type: dataset
title: Evaluation of Local LLMs for RO-Crate Metadata Enrichment
abstract: This experiment enriches an existing RO-Crate artifact with generated titles,
  descriptions, and keywords using locally hosted LLMs through Ollama. Different models
  and prompt context budgets are combined to evaluate how model choice and available
  artifact context influence metadata quality. Each run produces an enriched RO-Crate
  artifact together with run manifests, including token and runtime statistics, GPU
  and energy measurements, and automated comparisons against a human-written reference
  using BERTScore metric.
date-released: '2026-06-18'
authors:
